# __NAME_TITLE__ — tenant agent instance

A __TENANT__ agent instance grown against the Adaptive Marketing Agent OS
protocol. The protocol ships the invariants (schema + gates + validators +
run-state rails + GEB rails); this repo holds the generated, tenant-specific
composition and the pinned protocol copy. Runtime (Codex / Claude Code / Hermes
/ browser / local / MCP-backed) is your choice and is never durable agent state.

<directory>
agents/ - Generated agent instance for __TENANT__ (mounted agent, overlay, entrypoint, playbook workflows). L2 map: agents/AGENTS.md
</directory>

<directory>
agents/state/ - Run-state ledger for structured readbacks, proactive reusable-learning verdicts, verified GEB deltas, and reviewed tenant memory pointers
</directory>

<directory>
protocol/ - Pinned copy of the Adaptive Marketing Agent OS protocol (schema + gates + validators + reference roles). Never edited here; re-pin to upgrade. Version: protocol/VERSION
</directory>

<config>
protocol/VERSION - The pinned protocol name + version + source commit this instance validates against
</config>

法则: 极简·稳定·导航·版本精确

[PROTOCOL]: 变更时更新此头部，然后检查 AGENTS.md
